well im 29 been in vegas almost 3 years... i miss my close female friends that live back home. im not gay by far, just enjoy convo and being in a presence of a woman. If your bored, want to chill? smoke maybe? gamble? movie? sight seeing? drink? or just cruise around. please feel free to message me, i dont care if your pretty or ugly... fat or skinny... just be Sane/Respectful/open minded and just laid back... im not going to try and hookup with you. just looking for day to day friends to hangout with once in awhile or everyday...

Things i like;
Movies musicals concerts games gambling animals Firearms art ocean/lake cars/trucks shopping anytype of resturaunts bars or lounges, Clubs once in awhile kinda out growing it. sushi! playing woth my dog list goes on.
dislikes; 
liars, theifs 

so reply to this with some info about yourself? age/location/hobbies and maybe a pic? and i will do the same, dont be shy im not judging you one bit
